title: Surviving The Holidays with Dr. Stacy Cohen
description:
Lala is so freakin’ thankful for her air fryer! It was an “air fry everything” Thanksgiving at the Safe House (Lala’s new digs). Lala’s also excited for the upcoming #PumpRules reunion and spills a little tea in anticipation about her preparation and possible look. And then Dr. Stacy Cohen (the woman who started Lala on her path to sobriety) joins to help everyone navigate the stress, anxiety, and depression that typically accompanies the holiday season.
